        <item>
            <title>1.6.1 beta</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 11:58:24 +0100</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[<div style="font-family:'Arial'">
	<p>1.6.1</p>
	<div>
		<ul>
			<li>New Audio Player (e.g. no sound cuts when speeding up or slowing down)</li>
			<li>Beats Column in the Positions (can be enabled in settings, please restart the app afterwards)</li>
			<li>Beats are changeable, behaviour for the adaption of following positions can be chosen in settings</li>
			<li>Added an option to save the currently loaded song manually (CMD+S)</li>
			<li>App can now be minimized</li>
			<li>Fixed a bug when importing .infoexports with line breaks</li>
			<li>Many under the hood improvements</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>]]></description>
